c0c4d88e1924845c6bf906f514770","tid":1144533,"uid":61280,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-08T11:27:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有幅圖講以往各國GDP分佈，每次有國家GDP 接近美國，就會俾美國打殘， 90年代日本中左招。</blockquote><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">咪係！！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n所以架佬就話抵Q死嗟，支那GDP人人知鳩吹出黎都瀨野真真冇陰功囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />！！！！</span></strong></span></span>"},{"pid":"a88a60c0a23d6ede2813f6d704aa9ebcb32e4b51","tid":1144533,"uid":13281,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-08T11:27:17.000Z","msg":"炒樹皮期貨！快！"},{"pid":"7fd83ac745196f27a1f6221400a825225d6ae548","tid":1144533,"uid":120892,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-08T11:39:00.000Z","msg":"今次就真係撐環球個標題啦，民眾早就知有排玩，無人會信習維尼d咩一力承擔啦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2008314766fcae6afdd358e3dde41065ff0a84f0","tid":1144533,"uid":191926,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-08T11:44:55.000Z","msg":"諗起 赫魯曉夫<br />\n習近平：我會負責任 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n呢度有無人要我負全責<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n二十大之後，赫魯曉夫曾出席過不少黨的積極分子集會。在會上，他採取了知恥近乎勇的態度，總是承認自己以往確實目睹並知悉史達林時期犯下的許多罪惡行徑，然而又出於恐懼不敢站出來表示異議。有一次，在會上他接到了一張紙條，上面寫著：&lsquo;你們這些政治局委員怎麼竟然允許在大陸犯下如此嚴重的罪行呢?!&rsquo;赫魯曉夫念完條子後厲聲發問：&lsquo;這張沒署名的條子誰寫的，請起來!&rsquo;無人起立。接著他又重復了一遍，但是寫紙條的人還是沒有站出來。於是赫魯曉夫便說：&lsquo;寫條子的人害怕了。就是這麼回事，要是站起來反對史達林，我們也害怕呀。&rsquo;當然這種解釋並不全面，不過還算得上一個坦率老實的回答。"},{"pid":"f63ac483f07343563741ebfd4998f87f6d8dfbec","tid":1144533,"uid":160227,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-08T11:59:49.000Z","msg":"乜撚嘢係輿論界<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3c9073e6e725b969ccfc53e7cb5e52c03e33b0e2","tid":1144533,"uid":70786,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-08T12:14:40.000Z","msg":"(地球經濟中心) 外媒隨機街訪深圳民眾：沒聽說美國將加關稅<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1144692\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1144692</a><br />\n<br />\n有準備?<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"01a5e9a1339adcaedda534ada58c76db33877fd7","tid":1144533,"uid":21678,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-08T12:23:10.000Z","msg":"啲中文真係累贅到一塌糊塗"},{"pid":"940f139a45fdf66bca8a24dd96218a39f5fa189b","tid":1144533,"uid":12991,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"ced4f298ff1c0d1cd09a6878313268930830426d","tid":1144533,"uid":82301,"like":18,"dislike":0,"score":18,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-08T08:25:50.000Z","msg":"發燒再高一度，多燒一會，對中國的戰略上未必是很壞的事。<br />\n宜家咪燒壞腦囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-08T12:29:39.000Z","msg":"不嬲都壞<br />\n無分別 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6cd81c5b15d1275ed95c93994619db77df55940e","tid":1144533,"uid":129,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-08T12:46:42.000Z","msg":"個雜種食屎啦<br />\n你點撚樣負責呀<br />\n全國乞食你個仆街大魚大肉叫負責呀"},{"pid":"3dcc1d16c69383ccc3b8d68a781fad0c5358fd52","tid":1144533,"uid":61280,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-08T12:55:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>個雜種食屎啦<br />\n你點撚樣負責呀<br />\n全國乞食你個仆街大魚大肉叫負責呀</blockquote><br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">永帝嘅偶像當年大饑荒時代菜單：<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/tong